491
00:44:08,849 --> 00:44:12,219
Seo Woo,
I saw a lot of young people...

492
00:44:12,219 --> 00:44:16,090
taking photos and enjoying
their trip today. They looked happy.

493
00:44:19,260 --> 00:44:20,860
You and I are supposed to be
the only ones...

494
00:44:20,860 --> 00:44:22,429
who can have
a conversation with this.

495
00:44:23,269 --> 00:44:25,500
Either there was an error,
or it got hacked.

496
00:44:26,500 --> 00:44:29,199
What is the matter with you?
Why can't you keep it to yourself?

497
00:44:29,199 --> 00:44:30,369
Are you serious?

498
00:44:31,510 --> 00:44:32,840
I told you it can't be used
four counseling...

499
00:44:32,840 --> 00:44:35,480
if you can't block others
from accessing the machine.

500
00:44:38,880 --> 00:44:41,150
I changed the settings.
It won't get hacked.

501
00:44:42,150 --> 00:44:45,090
Try using it
and see if you can hack it.

502
00:44:45,420 --> 00:44:47,590
Does that mean it's hackable or not?

503
00:44:48,360 --> 00:44:49,429
Whatever.

504
00:45:17,949 --> 00:45:18,949
- My gosh.
- Send me an address in Seoul...

505
00:45:18,949 --> 00:45:20,090
where I can receive the parcel.

506
00:45:20,260 --> 00:45:22,789
- I'll do what you asked.
- Gosh, that's so complicated.

507
00:45:23,190 --> 00:45:24,659
Why can't she just use the address
she used last time?

508
00:45:37,070 --> 00:45:39,309
Hey, send me an address in Seoul.

509
00:45:39,480 --> 00:45:41,340
Then Seo Woo will do the mission.

510
00:45:55,420 --> 00:45:56,760
What are you staring at?

511
00:45:57,630 --> 00:45:58,889
The green leaves over there.

512
00:46:00,059 --> 00:46:02,130
I feel comfortable
whenever I look at anything green.

513
00:46:03,969 --> 00:46:05,900
You won't be able to see it
if I sit here.

514
00:46:05,900 --> 00:46:08,139
- Should I sit here instead?
- No, it's okay.

515
00:46:11,639 --> 00:46:12,909
Do you work nearby?

516
00:46:12,909 --> 00:46:14,840
Yes, it's only a few bus stops away.

517
00:46:15,909 --> 00:46:17,949
I called to make
an additional order.

518
00:46:17,949 --> 00:46:19,250
Do you like the bowls?

519
00:46:19,880 --> 00:46:21,820
The bowls go well with Korean food.

520
00:46:26,260 --> 00:46:27,789
Should I send them
to the same address?

521
00:46:27,789 --> 00:46:29,630
No, it's not there.

522
00:46:29,630 --> 00:46:31,659
Don't bring them yourself this time.
They're heavy.

523
00:46:32,530 --> 00:46:34,329
Let me check the address.

524
00:46:34,730 --> 00:46:37,199
What was the address again?
